divs: Sighting DetailsOn the morning of August 6 I awoke early to choke my chicken. (I am a chicken rancher and part time head of the [Profanity Deleted] moppers Union Local 384.) I heard a low thundering pulse and looked into the sky and saw a UFO with the words Suzy Licktenshtein on the side glowing in red. I grew woozy and then it seemed as though all time stopped. I woke up about 2 hours ago and one of my orifices is swollen - I won't tell you which one. I suspect that I was prodded by this Alien Sex Monster and I think I have been impregnated. Please pray that this is not so.
